 974: 
 975: They might as well have been following a pirate's treasure map. 
 976: 
 977: 'I know what you're thinking,' Nash said. 'If someone had told me this same story a week ago, I'd have thought about it the same way you do. But then, up until a couple of weeks ago, nobody even knew where the Santiago Manu script was.' 
