15770: 
15771: Fuck it, Doogie thought as, with a quick lunge, he reached deep inside the caiman's enormous jaws and wedged his Bowie knife in behind the G-11, positioning it vertically so that the knife's butt sat on the caiman's tongue while its blade rested up against the roof of the big beast's mouth. 
15772: 
15773: 'Eat this,' Doogie said as he swung his arm sideways, 
15774: 
15775: swiping the G-11 out of the giant reptile's mouth. 
15776: 
15777: The response was instantaneous. 
15778: 
